Ripple.BoundedUniversality.BGP.HeadlineUnconditional
---------------------------------
Concrete headline frontier for the shifted warm-gain route.

This file fixes the structural/numeric headline parameters and discharges the
finite-horizon and polynomial-field hypotheses.  The remaining hypotheses are
the proof-producing analytic frontier; they are kept explicit rather than
hidden behind an axiom.
