the family-dependent F1 surface at the N-parametric solution family
`paper3HeadlineSolFamN` (params `bgpParamsN`: `cμ = 1000·bgpScale`,
`cα = 300·bgpScale`, `bgpScale = N₀ + 4`), with every hull scaled by
