`paper3F1_coordMultiplier_le_BUpow_coarseDelta`, and the two generic tube
induction engines (they take the coordinate function `u` as an argument).

⚠️ SOUNDNESS TRIAGE OF THE FIVE F1 ANALYTIC INPUTS AT THE N FAMILY
(2026-07-10 falsity sweep; numeric sketches in `RUN_LOG_automode.md`):

* (1/5) window bootstrap, (2/5) cycle-0 endpoint: TRUE at the scaled hulls —
  PROVED below (first-exit bootstraps at the `1/3` branch-eval tube).
* (3/5) inter-read source cap: FALSE at the original `ws (j+1)` endpoint
