/-- Halt-centered bad-pair reduction for the Hoff edge TV integrand: with the
center at the old or new winner and `henc` (the two winner halt targets
agree), the winner terms vanish from the halt-centered form and every
remaining bad-view term is the per-view selector ODE right-hand side times a
