/-- **Crude edge `z−u` envelope** on `[wr j, 2πj+π]` at the word-coupled
family: the u-tube persists (Seg C edge tube), so the mix target stays in
the crude affine branch hull; `z` enters within `CwinDefN` of `u` (Seg C
window envelope at `wr j`) and is trapped in the hull box; the difference
